question: Display Boeing aircrafts and Airbus aircrafts with 180 seats.
sql_query1:
SELECT Boeing.Model
FROM Boeing
WHERE Boeing.Number_of_seats = 180
UNION
SELECT Airbus.Model
FROM Airbus
WHERE Airbus.Number_of_seats = 180
sql_query2:
SELECT Boeing.Model
FROM Boeing
UNION
SELECT Airbus.Model
FROM Airbus
WHERE Airbus.Number_of_seats = 180
interpretation1: Can you show both Boeing and Airbus aircraft models that have 180 seats?
interpretation2: Provide a list of Boeing aircraft and also display airbus aircraft with 180 seats.
